# qfg-ascii: skip browser qfg-seed generated routed circuit
#
# Browser/GLSL-native static 3-bit ripple-carry adder with edge-visible result ports.
# Generated by tools/generate-browser-static-ripple-adder-qfg.cjs.
# It emits only QFG primitive cells and boundary input frames.
# Result bits are also routed to ordinary external edge readout lanes.
# Stable-surface mode keeps 2-bit and 3-bit adders in the same 64x64 envelope.

